# Food Menu CRUD API

A RESTful API built using Node.js, Express.js, and MySQL to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on food menu items.

## Features

* Add new food items to the menu
* Retrieve all menu items
* Update existing food records
* Delete menu items
* MySQL database integration
* REST API architecture
* JSON request and response handling

## Technologies Used

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MySQL
* CORS

## API Endpoints

### Create Food Item

```http
POST /post
```

### Get All Food Items

```http
GET /get
```

### Update Food Item

```http
PUT /update/:id
```

### Delete Food Item

```http
DELETE /delete/:id
```

## Database

Database: `foods`

Table: `menu`

Fields:

* id
* foodName
* foodCost
* foodType
* softDrink
* costOfDrink

